The paper discusses the study of locomotion in robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of dynamical systems and soft matter physics, which suggests that it could also fall under the categories of systems and control (cs.SY), materials science (cs.MA), and computational engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of simplified theoretical models, which could also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) if these models are visualized or simulated.
